divs: Sighting DetailsI and my girlfriend went outside for a smoke.Thats when she said whats that in the sky?I look up and see this saturn shaped object with blue red, yellow, and other colors.The colors were moving in a counterclockwise movement. Then thats when I saw two spheres or oval shaped ufos flying below the first ufo thy were the same color as space but darker a bit.these two ufos would fly to the bottom of the first one and the back to the ground moving all most to fast to see but we both could see them!!After 20 mins she and I went inside after seeing the ufos move north and up in the sky.Then it looked like a star in the sky!!!
